note: I'm a cool cat. I am a loving son and brother and a loyal friend. I am proudly queer and welcoming to others from different walks of life. I am a hard worker, intent on staying open to growth opportunities my entire life. Creating art, being in nature on a mountain hike, dancing and singing to my heart's desire, and spending time with those I love and care for are the activities that bring me the most joy. My expressions of joy are smiles and laughs, song and dance!
